Package edu.wpi.first.networktables

Class ValueListenerPoller

java.lang.Object
edu.wpi.first.networktables.ValueListenerPoller
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable
public final class ValueListenerPoller
extends Object
implements AutoCloseable
Value change listener. This queues value change events matching the specified mask. Code using the listener must periodically call readQueue() to read the events.
